title: Freeman survives tough upbringing to emerge as Falcons star
text:
> Georgia Freeman survives tough upbringing to emerge as Falcons star Atlanta Falcons running back Devonta Freeman (24) scores a touchdown as Washington Redskins strong safety Trenton Robinson (34) and Washington Redskins cornerback Bashaud Breeland (26) defend during the second half of an NFL football game, Sunday, Oct. 11, 2015, in Atlanta.
